[Lumpy skin disease continues to spread regionally, now affecting the FYR of Macedonia.

Recently, Bulgaria reported lumpy skin disease, where to date 9 outbreaks have been reported. See event summary and map at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=20044. - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4177438,22550.]
